**Navigation**

**Palo Alto Cortex XDR**

- [Alerts](#/dashboard/panw_cortex_xdr-a349f1e6-6762-4a54-9512-e22b32acb9d9)
- [Incidents](#/dashboard/panw_cortex_xdr-10c6821e-1f7c-4ea6-acf8-e667ab0f03ce)
- **Events**

**Overview**

This dashboard provides in-depth visibility into events forwarded by Palo Alto Networks Cortex XDR, equipped with a Control Panel for filtering by Operating System and Network Protocol. It includes visualizations such as Top 10 File Names by Highest Events, Top 10 File Owners by Highest Events, Events by File Type, Events by File Group Name, Top 10 Destination IPs by Highest Events, Top 10 Source IPs by Highest Events, Events by Network Protocol, Events by Host Name, Events by Agent OS Type, along with Process Essential Details and Event Essential Details for comprehensive event-level analysis.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/panw_cortex_xdr-2.2.0/overview)
